# Images and large binary files
BrandX_cards/images/
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.tiff
*.tif
*.heic
*.heif
*.cr2
*.cr3
*.nef
*.arw
*.dng
*.psd
*.psb

# Keep specific assets
!v2/assets/icon.png
!v2/assets/icon.icns

# Build artifacts
script/dist/
script/build/
v2/dist/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python
*.egg-info/
*.egg
venv/
.venv/

# Node (if ever used)
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Playwright
playwright-report/
test-results/
playwright/.cache/

# Backlog edits (user's local state)
*_edits.json

# Large archives and videos
*.zip
*.mov
*.mp4
*.pdf
.git_old

# Config with API keys (NEVER commit)
config.json
config.local.json
v2/frontend/config.json

# Secrets folder — OAuth credentials, refresh tokens, anything sensitive.
# NEVER commit. git автоматически проигнорит всё внутри.
secrets/
**/secrets/
*.credentials.json
client_secret_*.json
*-token.json
*-tokens.json

# Large legacy HTML files with embedded images
BrandX_карточки товара.html
BrandX_карточки_товара_v2.html
_snapshots/

# PII / private docs — никогда не коммитить
*-pii.md
*-private.md
contacts.md
**/contacts.md

# --- PII safeguard (added 2026-04-24 after filter-repo scrub) ---
# Block accidental commits of client-name files. If you need a legitimate
# file with one of these tokens, override per-file with `git add -f <path>`.
**/*ekonika*
**/*Ekonika*
**/*EKONIKA*
**/*Эконика*
**/*ЭКОНИКА*
**/*эконика*
**/*moiseeva*
**/*Moiseeva*
**/*Моисеева*
**/*markformelle*
**/*Markformelle*
**/*MarkFormelle*
**/*MARKFORMELLE*
**/*Mark Formelle*
**/*Марк Формель*
# Allow placeholders/labels (already-scrubbed output):
!**/client-a*
!**/tester-a*
!**/surname-hidden*
# --- end PII safeguard ---
